## Group theory from the left axioms

Classical first-order equational benchmark (TPTP GRP family). Given only
_left_ identity, _left_ inverse, and associativity, prove the corresponding
_right_ facts.

```elixir
group_axioms = """
thf(o_t, type, o: $i>$i>$i).
thf(e_t, type, e: $i).
thf(i_t, type, i: $i>$i).
thf(assoc, axiom, ![X:$i, Y:$i, Z:$i]:
  o @ (o @ X @ Y) @ Z = o @ X @ (o @ Y @ Z)).
thf(left_id, axiom, ![X:$i]: o @ e @ X = X).
thf(left_inv, axiom, ![X:$i]: o @ (i @ X) @ X = e).
"""
```

<!-- livebook:{"output":true} -->

```
"thf(o_t, type, o: $i>$i>$i).\nthf(e_t, type, e: $i).\nthf(i_t, type, i: $i>$i).\nthf(assoc, axiom, ![X:$i, Y:$i, Z:$i]:\n  o @ (o @ X @ Y) @ Z = o @ X @ (o @ Y @ Z)).\nthf(left_id, axiom, ![X:$i]: o @ e @ X = X).\nthf(left_inv, axiom, ![X:$i]: o @ (i @ X) @ X = e).\n"
```

**Right identity from left axioms.**

```elixir
race(
  fn opts ->
    prove(
      ~p"""
      #{group_axioms}
      thf(conj, conjecture, ![X:$i]: o @ X @ e = X).
      """,
      opts
    )
  end,
  configs
)
```

<!-- livebook:{"output":true} -->

```

